{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"12587-kashti-muyo","title":"कश्टी मुयो","description":"ह्या मुयांच्या फाटी फाटीं या. ल्हान वाचप्यांक त्यो शेर्त गुंतोवन दवरतल्यो. ‘भोंवतणचीं जनावरां’ ह्या चार पुस्तकांच्या माळेंतलें हें एक पुस्तक.","language":"Konkani","langCode":"kok","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Chetan Acharya"],"illustrators":["Deepa Balsavar"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Konkani Bhasha Mandal","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/12587-kashti-muyo"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/704670/size3/241eb27666dc624a6d0b5f5b2871e868.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/704670/size6/241eb27666dc624a6d0b5f5b2871e868.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13113/size6/6fdb6384a32650b9a5c3fa18e2911571.jpg","text":"पळय पळय! हांव हे रांकेंत चवथी आसां.  दिसता न्ही?","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13114/size6/5a69c82d463c123769b132250d52614e.jpg","text":"दावो-उजवो, दावो-उजवो. आमी शांतपणान रांकेंत चलतात.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13115/size6/d76a595d6193d51826a7f7fc650ed77a.jpg","text":"म्हाका एक गजाल येवजल्या. सामकें नेटान वचूंक जाय जाल्यार पांयांक चाकां लावप.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13116/size6/7534de2d1ce6d49e268aab3236a1920e.jpg","text":"बाकीच्या जनावरां वरी आमी आवाज करिनात. आमची भास वासाची.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13117/size6/c1346b41f03c604b61cc7919576135f7.jpg","text":"एके तरेचो वास म्हणटा, “म्हजे फाटल्यान हे वटेन येयात. हांगा खावड आसा.”","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13118/size6/16a843e35736981d828a9e6427f6ccc6.jpg","text":"दुसरो वास म्हणटा, “अरिश्ट! थंय वचनाकात.”","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13119/size6/830248e8b11e9e7916ec154f0df68215.jpg","text":"तुमचे वरीच म्हाका केक आनी सगळें गोड खाण आवडटा.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13120/size6/8745c7edb8e0008518f0a4f305717985.jpg","text":"तुमकां म्हजी ताकद पळोवंक जाय?\nहांव ल्हान दिसतां आसत, पूण हांव खूब बळिश्ट.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13121/size6/2d6959400605bcf6866869e09e411f4b.jpg","text":"दार बंद आसल्यारूय चलता.\nहांव इल्लेशे खाचींतल्यान वचपाक शकतां.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13664/size6/a43c28fffeb1ae739f2f0952dfd98fb0.jpg","text":"विस्वास बसता जाल्यार पळय, पूण एके रोयणींत आमी शेंकड्यांनी मुयो आनंदान रावतात.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13123/size6/2a921d6470d9372bd2697500681c4558.jpg","text":"चलात थोडे नवे शब्द शिकुया.\n ल्हान  - व्हड\n मंद - गतीन\n मोटवो - लांब\n बारीक - मोटो\n घट - मोव\n बोवाळ - शांतताय\nहांगा थोडे शब्द आसात आनी ताचे विरोधार्थी शब्द आसात. तुज्यान तांचीं वाक्यां तयार करूंक जायत?\nदेखीक \"मूय\nल्हान आसा; हती व्हड आसा.\"\n\"मुये वरी वावुरपी\" अशें म्हणल्यार खूब काम करपी अशी तोखणाय करप.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":153}}